work_on_weakness: Suggestion 1: Improve delivery time by optimizing delivery routes and employing more delivery staff to handle high demand times.
Suggestion 2: Invest in insulated delivery bags to ensure food stays warm during transit.
work_on_threats: Suggestion 1: Invest in faster and more efficient delivery options to reduce wait times and ensure food arrives hot.
Suggestion 2: Improve the functionality of the app to allow real-time tracking of food delivery, which will add to customer satisfaction.
